b)." Lilly, Eli and Company  (2018):', 'Cyclosporine, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Tocilizumab, Secukinumab, Ravulizumab, Mycophenolic acid, Methotrexate, Tacrolimus, Abatacept, Apremilast, Inebilizumab, More', 'Pertuzumab, Cetuximab, Avelumab, Trastuzumab emtansine, Panitumumab, Ipilimumab, Necitumumab, Bevacizumab, Dostarlimab, Amivantamab, Ramucirumab, More', 1767369485);
