0095/', '[1] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[2] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0', 'Methotrimeprazine, Quetiapine, Asenapine, Thiothixene, Pimavanserin, Lumateperone, Clozapine, Olanzapine, Aripiprazole, Loxapine, Molindone, More', 'Tinidazole, Ascorbic acid, Simeprevir, Rosuvastatin, Sulfadiazine, Lactic acid, Mitapivat, Methazolamide, Clindamycin, Ciclopirox, Darunavir, More', 1767369485);
